      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Richard Keys is a non-executive member of the departmental boards at the Department for Transport and the Department for International Development. He is also a non-executive Director at Wessex Water Services, NATS Holdings and Merrill Lynch International.</p>

<p>He is a former senior partner of PricewaterhouseCoopers where latterly he held the role of Global Chief Accountant. Richard also chairs the board of Glaziers Hall Ltd and was formerly a non-executive director at Sainsburyâ€™s Bank.</p>

</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4471">
            <h1 id="non-executive-board-member-dft">Non-executive board member, DfT</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Non-executive board members provide the Department for Transport with strategic advice, support and challenge. They also attend departmental board meetings and meet with the management team.</p>
</div>
